  "description": "VEX v1.0 Stable is the first release version of the VEX dataset aligned with the downstream benchmark and modeling pipeline. It contains one record per student short-answer response, with anonymized identifiers, cleaned question and answer text, question metadata, a normalized ordinal grade, a train/test split, and label provenance indicating gold versus silver supervision. The dataset is predominantly German; a small minority of responses originate from international students and may contain English or mixed German-English text. This minority is estimated to be approximately 3% or less of the dataset.",
